A massive industrial gear system rendered in warm sepia tones and aged paper textures, where some gears spin smoothly with golden light emanating from their centers while others are rusted and jammed with cobwebs. In the foreground, a single small but brilliantly polished gear connects to the larger mechanism, its teeth perfectly aligned and glowing with amber energy, creating a ripple effect of movement through the previously stuck components. The composition shows a cross-section view like a vintage mechanical diagram, with delicate crosshatching and weathered edges suggesting an old engineering blueprint. Steam wisps curl through the scene, and scattered around the base are tiny detailed tools—wrenches, oil cans, and measuring instruments—all rendered in the style of 1920s technical illustrations with rich brown and cream color palette.
